defined_text = { 
	name = Disp_ProdLayer
	random = no
	text = { 
		localisation_key = Disp_Prod_01
		trigger = { 
			OR = { 
				is_variable_equal = { 
					which = ayx
					value = 0
				}
				is_variable_equal = { 
					which = ayx
					value = 1
				}
			}
		}
	}
}

defined_text = { 
	name = Disp_Cashcrop
	random = no
	text = { 
		localisation_key = Cashcrop_Tea
		trigger = { 
			has_province_flag = tea
		}
	}
	text = { 
		localisation_key = Cashcrop_Sugar
		trigger = { 
			has_province_flag = sugar
		}
	}
	text = { 
		localisation_key = Cashcrop_Coffee
		trigger = { 
			has_province_flag = coffee
		}
	}
	text = { 
		localisation_key = Cashcrop_Cacao
		trigger = { 
			has_province_flag = cacao
		}
	}
	text = { 
		localisation_key = Cashcrop_Coca
		trigger = { 
			has_province_flag = coca
		}
	}
	text = { 
		localisation_key = Cashcrop_Beer
		trigger = { 
			has_province_flag = beer
		}
	}
	text = { 
		localisation_key = Cashcrop_Honey
		trigger = { 
			has_province_flag = honey
		}
	}
	text = { 
		localisation_key = Cashcrop_Wine
		trigger = { 
			has_province_flag = wine
		}
	}
	text = { 
		localisation_key = Cashcrop_Olives
		trigger = { 
			has_province_flag = olive
		}
	}
	text = { 
		localisation_key = Cashcrop_Fruits
		trigger = { 
			has_province_flag = fruits
		}
	}
	text = { 
		localisation_key = Cashcrop_Incense
		trigger = { 
			has_province_flag = incense
		}
	}
	text = { 
		localisation_key = Cashcrop_Dates
		trigger = { 
			has_province_flag = dates
		}
	}
	text = { 
		localisation_key = Cashcrop_Kola
		trigger = { 
			has_province_flag = kola
		}
	}
	text = { 
		localisation_key = Cashcrop_Cashcrop
		trigger = { 
			OR = { 
				has_province_flag = cashcrop
				NOT = { 
					OR = { 
						has_province_flag = tea
						has_province_flag = sugar
						has_province_flag = coffee
						has_province_flag = cacao
						has_province_flag = coca
						has_province_flag = beer
						has_province_flag = honey
						has_province_flag = wine
						has_province_flag = olive
						has_province_flag = fruits
						has_province_flag = incense
						has_province_flag = dates
						has_province_flag = kola
					}
				}
			}
		}
	}
}
defined_text = { 
	name = Disp_Fiber
	random = no
	text = { 
		localisation_key = Cashcrop_Fiber
		trigger = { 
			NOT = { 
				has_province_flag = hemp
			}
		}
	}
	text = { 
		localisation_key = Cashcrop_Hemp
		trigger = { 
			has_province_flag = hemp
		}
	}
}

defined_text = { 
	name = Disp_Prod2S7Sply9
	random = no
	text = { 
		localisation_key = Disp_Prod2S7Sply9B
		trigger = { 
			check_variable = { 
				which = evg
				value = 0.001
			}
			AND = { 
				OR = { 
					AND = { 
						check_variable = { 
							which = btv
							value = 16
						}
						NOT = { 
							check_variable = { 
								which = btv
								value = 19
							}
						}
					}
					is_variable_equal = { 
						which = btv
						value = 41
					}
				}
			}
		}
	}
	text = {

		trigger = { 
			check_variable = { 
				which = evg
				value = 0.001
			}
		}

defined_text = { 
	name = Disp_Prod2S10Sply9
	random = no
	text = { 
		localisation_key = Disp_Prod2S10Sply9B
		trigger = { 
			check_variable = { 
				which = hhw
				value = 0.001
			}
			AND = { 
				OR = { 
					AND = { 
						check_variable = { 
							which = gzn
							value = 16
						}
						NOT = { 
							check_variable = { 
								which = gzn
								value = 19
							}
						}
					}
					is_variable_equal = { 
						which = gzn
						value = 41
					}
				}
			}
		}
	}
	text = { 
		localisation_key = Disp_Prod2S10Sply9
		trigger = { 
			check_variable = { 
				which = hhw
				value = 0.001
			}
		}
	}

	random = no
	text = { 
		localisation_key = Disp_Comma
		trigger = { 
			OR = { 
				check_variable = { 
					which = ekt
					value = 0.001
				}
				check_variable = { 
					which = eky
					value = 0.001
				}
			}
		}
	}
}
